慈悲
====

HTTP server for bypassing censorship

Why?
----

1. Proxy protocols (like openvpn+cloak, vless+reality+xhttp) are an overkill for most situations
2. It's hard to get xray/sing-box working on free servers (like railway and render)
3. A normal person doesn't deserve being carried through 7 circles of hell just to get a proxy that they'll dispose of anyway

Pros
----

1. No overhead for TCP 3 way handshakes to proxy for each connection due to multiplexing
2. Easily deployable
